  - 873
By: Sri Sankarâchârya
---
The modifications of the intellect, called Tight knowledge’, ‘doubtful
knowledge’ and ‘false knowledge’, deviate from their existence. There is one
and the same Consciousness in all of them. The differences are due to the
modifications.
